  <GeneDef ParentName="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneDeathless_Base" Name="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneDeathless_Undead" Abstract="True">
	<labelShortAdj>undead</labelShortAdj>
	<description>Carriers of this gene accumulate resurgent cells with age. In the event of death, these cells are immediately activated and, in a fairly short time, completely restore damaged or even destroyed tissues.</description>
	<iconPath>WVC/UI/Genes/Gene_Deathless_v0</iconPath>
	<selectionWeight>0.0022</selectionWeight>
	<displayOrderInCategory>1275</displayOrderInCategory>
	<geneClass>WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.Gene_Undead</geneClass>
	<biostatCpx>0</biostatCpx>
	<biostatArc>0</biostatArc>
	<biostatMet>0</biostatMet>
	<customEffectDescriptions>
	  <li>In case of death, after some time the carrier of the gene will be resurrected, completely healthy and without damage.</li>
	  <li>If the carrier’s &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;brain was destroyed&lt;/color&gt;, then the carrier of the gene &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;loses backstory and all experience in skills&lt;/color&gt;.</li>
	  <li>Recovery will take (*DateTime)2-8 days(/DateTime)</li>
	</customEffectDescriptions>
	<symbolPack>
	  <wholeNameSymbols>
		<li><symbol>undead</symbol></li>
	  </wholeNameSymbols>
	  <prefixSymbols>
		<li><symbol>un</symbol></li>
		<li><symbol>mortal</symbol></li>
		<li><symbol>im</symbol></li>
	  </prefixSymbols>
	  <suffixSymbols>
		<li><symbol>dead</symbol></li>
		<li><symbol>im</symbol></li>
		<li><symbol>mortal</symbol></li>
	  </suffixSymbols>
	</symbolPack>
	<resourceLossPerDay>0.41</resourceLossPerDay>
	<exclusionTags>
	  <li>WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneDeathless_Undead</li>
	</exclusionTags>
	<modExtensions>
		<li Class="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.GeneExtension_Giver">
			<childBackstoryDef>WVC_RacesBiotech_Amnesia_Child</childBackstoryDef>
			<adultBackstoryDef>WVC_RacesBiotech_Amnesia_Adult</adultBackstoryDef>
			<hediffDefs>
				<li>WVC_Resurgent_UndeadResurrectionRecovery</li>
			</hediffDefs>
		</li>
	</modExtensions>
  </GeneDef>

