  <GeneDef ParentName="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneDeathless_Base">
	<defName>WVC_DeadCat</defName>
	<label>deadcat</label>
	<description>Carriers of this gene cannot die. No matter how severe their wounds are, they always rise from the dead. The only way to kill them is to destroy their entire body.</description>
	<iconColor>(60, 60, 60)</iconColor>
	<iconPath>WVC/UI/Genes/Gene_DeadCat_v0</iconPath>
	<displayOrderInCategory>1272</displayOrderInCategory>
	<geneClass>WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.Gene_Undead</geneClass>
	<biostatCpx>7</biostatCpx>
	<biostatArc>2</biostatArc>
	<biostatMet>0</biostatMet>
	<customEffectDescriptions>
	  <li>In case of death, after some time the carrier will be resurrected, completely healthy and without damage.</li>
	  <li>If the carrier’s &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;brain was destroyed&lt;/color&gt;, then the carrier of the gene &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;loses backstory and all experience in skills&lt;/color&gt;.</li>
	  <li>&lt;color=#ff8585&gt;The only way to kill the carrier is to destroy the body.&lt;/color&gt;</li>
	</customEffectDescriptions>
	<exclusionTags>
	  <li>WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneDeathless_Undead</li>
	</exclusionTags>
	<modExtensions>
		<li Class="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.GeneExtension_Giver">
			<childBackstoryDef>WVC_RacesBiotech_Amnesia_Child</childBackstoryDef>
			<adultBackstoryDef>WVC_RacesBiotech_Amnesia_Adult</adultBackstoryDef>
		</li>
	</modExtensions>
  </GeneDef>

